*Mislila* je da bi mogla da postigne više. (She thought she could achieve more.)

*Mislile* su da će biti uspešne. (They thought they would be successful.)

Često se *mislilo* da će biti bolje. (It was often thought that it would be better.)

*Misli* da je to rešenje. (She thinks that is the solution.)

Ona *misli* da je sve u redu. (She thinks everything is alright.)